	"displayName": "GPThemes - ChatGPT Customization & Layout Tweaks",
	"description": "Redesign ChatGPT: custom accent colors, fonts, and layouts â€” with widescreen mode, chat width sliders, expandable chatbox, hide header/footer & more.",
